<paragraph blockId="16.[166,794,1527,1638]" pageId="16" pageNumber="347">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[166,254,1527,1551]" pageId="16" pageNumber="347">Habitat</emphasis>
. This species lives mostly amongst the brown alga 
<taxonomicName box="[166,323,1557,1580]" class="Phaeophyceae" family="Sargassaceae" genus="Sargassum" kingdom="Chromista" order="Fucales" pageId="16" pageNumber="347" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis box="[166,283,1557,1580]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="347">Sargassum</emphasis>
sp.
